# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SECURITY CHECKLIST - قائمة التحقق الأمني
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# ✅ Before deploying to production:
# 
# 1. [ ] Change SECRET_KEY to a new random string
# 2. [ ] Set DEBUG=False
# 3. [ ] Update ALLOWED_HOSTS with your domain
# 4. [ ] Use strong DB_PASSWORD (16+ characters)
# 5. [ ] Rotate Twilio credentials if exposed
# 6. [ ] Set correct CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS
# 7. [ ] Set CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS for your domain
# 8. [ ] Change ADMIN_URL to something secret
# 9. [ ] Enable HTTPS (SSL certificate)
# 10. [ ] Set up regular backups
# 11. [ ] Configure firewall rules
# 12. [ ] Enable monitoring/logging
# 13. [ ] Review security headers
# 14. [ ] Test authentication flows
# 15. [ ] Perform security audit
#
